'''''Geastrum coronatum''''' is an inedible species of [[mushroom]] belonging to the genus ''[[Geastrum]]'', or earthstar fungi. [[Christian Hendrik Persoon]] published the first [[species description|description]] of ''Geastrum coronatum'' in 1801.<ref>{{cite book |author=Persoon CH. |year=1801 |title=Synopsis Methodica Fungorum (Göttingen) |volume=1 |pages=132–133}}</ref>
